{"tid":1990474,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"本港二手樓價創8周新高","createTime":"2020-04-26T16:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T03:24:41.000Z","uid":135867,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"def6f09f68dd352f344e40c430e08b9270cd7da8","tid":1990474,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:59:08.000Z","msg":"反映本港二手樓價走勢的中原城市領先指數最新報175.68，按周升0.47%，創8周新高，中小型單位指數同大型屋苑指數升0.5%以上。大型單位樓價靠穩。<br />\n<br />\n各地區當中，港島區樓價指數升0.89%，結束3周連跌，九龍區樓價升0.81%，新界西就升0.46%，新界東跌0.03%。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產表示，樓價有止跌跡象，復活節長期後二手成交持續，樓價走勢有望出現變化。<br />\n<br />\n本周公布的指數根據的成交，有約70%在上月底至本月初簽訂臨時買賣合約。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522547-20200424.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522547-20200424.htm&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4FEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=525d24b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522547-20200424.htm&h=842071b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522547-20200424.htm</a>"},{"pid":"72d3cd81f9dafdd66949c4617860311886952257","tid":1990474,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8800fa138b7df38c119c733cfbbd9cc84727e1c","tid":1990474,"uid":115337,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"廢炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121464967487694035798c4b2758ed544b314b4f","tid":1990474,"uid":3179,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:56:00.000Z","msg":"呢一世都唔洗旨意買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c761f081b80c23fbb71f440b91a64551191b89b8","tid":1990474,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"121464967487694035798c4b2758ed544b314b4f","tid":19904